 2009-05342009-04-10,  ,  ,  PMO
PrecisAdvise that the confidences of the Queen's Privy Council for Canada that are contained in certain documents may be made available for the purpose of the proceedings of the Commission of Inquiry into Certain Allegations Respecting Business and Financial Dealings Between Karlheinz Schreiber and the Right Honourable Mulroney, P.C., and that any individual may testify in respect of the confidences of the Queen's Privy Council for Canada for the purposes of the proceedings of the said Commission.
